OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776355854
OL,3,CMan knocked down by a vehicle after
OL,4,Cserious assault with a wrench
OL,6,FA man has been taken to hospital after
OL,7,Fbeing knocked down by a vehicle when
OL,8,Fhe tried to escape following a serious
OL,9,Fassault with a wheel brace and a
OL,10,Fwrench.
OL,12,FPolice in Newry are appealing for
OL,13,Finformation following a report of the
OL,14,Fassault in the Craigmore View area, on
OL,15,FWednesday 15th April.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
