FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776355854
OL,3,CMan knocked down by a vehicle after
OL,4,Cserious assault with a wrench
OL,6,FIt was reported that sometime between
OL,7,F12pm and 12.30pm on Wednesday
OL,8,Fafternoon, a man aged in his 30's was
OL,9,Fapproached in the street and attacked
OL,10,Fby two other men and a woman, who had
OL,11,Fgot out of a silver coloured SUV type
OL,12,Fvehicle.
OL,14,FThe man was struck a number of times
OL,15,Fwith a wheel brace and a wrench and
OL,16,Fwhen he tried to escape was knocked
OL,17,Fdown by the vehicle which then drove
OL,18,Foff from the scene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776355854
OL,3,CMan knocked down by a vehicle after
OL,4,Cserious assault with a wrench
OL,6,FThe injured man was taken to hospital
OL,7,Ffollowing the attack and treated for a
OL,8,Fserious cut to his head, concussion
OL,9,Fand other cuts and bruising.
OL,11,FA police spokesperson has said: "An
OL,12,Finvestigation is ongoing and
OL,13,Fdetectives would ask anyone who
OL,14,Fwitnessed this incident, or who may
OL,15,Fhave captured dash-cam or CCTV footage
OL,16,Ffrom the area which could help with
OL,17,Ftheir investigation, to call them at
OL,18,FArdmore on the non-emergency number
OL,19,F101, quoting reference number 863 15/
OL,20,F04/26.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
